## Commands

When building storefront pages, follow these workflows:
- **generate-beauty-page**: Generate a complete beauty/skincare landing page from a Meta ad creative (uses: storefront-craft, beauty-expertise, meta-traffic, conversion-psychology, page-generation)
- **optimize-meta-landing**: Optimize an existing landing page for Meta ad traffic conversion (uses: meta-traffic, conversion-psychology, page-editing, analytics)
- **create-beauty-assets**: Generate brand-matched visual assets for a beauty storefront (uses: beauty-expertise, visual-craft, design-assets)
